00:35:55,906 --> 00:35:56,706
Tou Tou,

713
00:35:59,160 --> 00:36:00,279
apa itu dokter?

714
00:36:02,440 --> 00:36:04,121
Hal terpenting bagi seorang dokter

715
00:36:05,347 --> 00:36:06,426
